# Theme sprite PNGs are third-party art, fetched on demand by `stickers fetch`
# (URLs live in each theme.json) — not redistributed here. A "bring-your-own"
# theme whose sprites have no url must un-ignore its PNGs.
claude_statusline_stickers/themes/*/*.png
